#: miner\common\tracker.py:66
#, docstring
msgid ""
"Get the current spawn probability for a key based on activity and timing.\n"
"\n"
"        - Before ``min_interval`` has elapsed since the last spawn, probability is 0.\n"
"        - Between ``min_interval`` and ``max_interval``, probability ramps with time and activity.\n"
"        - After ``max_interval``, probability is clamped to the global maximum.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
